											</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Really liked this &#8211; another hellish inferno story, all the worse for it&#8217;s realism.</p>
<p>I enjoyed the grimness of the description &#8211; caked organic nasty food vibes. </p>
<p>Seems deeply appropriate for the Christmas season&#8217;s family cooking experiences.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

				<div class="reply"><a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/2010/12/21/feeling-hot/?replytocom=1062#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm( "div-comment-1062", "1062", "respond", "622" )' aria-label='Reply to elementalsystems'>Reply</a></div>			</article><!-- .comment-body -->
